<h1>Schedule</h1>

<p>The following schedule will be updated frequently with reference material and 
a more precise indication of what has been covered in class. 
Please note that the slides available for this website are slightly different from
the ones used in class since the latter have more explanatory material.
The topics for future lectures are here only as indication and may change as the course progresses. </p>

